'''Frak''' or '''frack''' was a profanity popular on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]]. It was also used in modifiers such as "frakkin".

It was also used by one of the guards at [[Cog Hive Seven]] in [[32 BBY/Legends|32 BBY]].

It was also sometimes shouted by [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]], [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|rebel]] troopers, [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]], and [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] in certain situations, such as when getting hit during a battle.

